snippet.title: NEW Johnny Depp Info/Far Cry 6/Horizon Forbidden West And More! - Chivalry 2 Livestream
snippet.description:
There was a bunch of stuff that happened this week, including brand new Amber Heard/Johnny Depp Legal news, Far Cry 6, Horizon Forbidden West, Dying Light 2 and more! Let's discuss it all all while playing Chivalry 2! Let me know what you think and make sure to subscribe to the channel for more content!! #JusticeForJohnnyDepp #Chivalry2 #HorizonForbiddenWest
